videos.headline: Rhode Island's Maye Toure nails a short floater
videos.description: Maye Toure drills a short floater off of a Dolly Cairns dime to score early for the Rams.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Rhode Island's Maye Toure nails a short floater) 2023/02/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: VCU's Tamaya Lewis-Eutsey protects the rim
videos.description: Tamaya Lewis-Eutsey stands her ground and blocks Ines Debroise for the  Rams.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (VCU's Tamaya Lewis-Eutsey protects the rim) 2023/02/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Rhode Island's Madison Hattix-Covington drills a fast break 3
videos.description: Dolly Cairns finds Madison Hattix-Covington on the fast break for a quick three-pointer to build their lead vs. VCU.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Rhode Island's Madison Hattix-Covington drills a fast break 3) 2023/02/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Rhode Island's Sayawni Lassiter shows off with a half-court bounce pass
videos.description: Sayawni Lassiter finds Dolly Cairns and dimes her with a nice half-court bounce pass for an easy bucket.
